4Geeks Academy offers an AI and Machine Learning Engineer bootcamp, designed for beginners with no prior experience. Over 16 weeks, students will learn Python, SQL, and key libraries such as Pandas and Numpy. The curriculum covers machine learning models, including supervised and unsupervised learning, alongside real-world case studies. The program includes three classes per week, with a maximum class size of 12. Participants receive a recognized certificate upon completion. Bilingual options are available for the course content, with live classes in the campus language. For more details, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). stop